  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2281555">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2281555/" class="title-link">英国新书介绍#11 D-Day: The Battle for Normandy</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2281555"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/newlight/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1425949-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/newlight/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">newlight</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-28"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-28 22:19:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2281555_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书我过去已经做了一点介绍，而且在英国畅销书非小说类精装本排行榜上占据榜首好几个星期，但还是想再推荐一次。  这部差不多600页厚的书，我用一点一点的零碎时间慢慢地读，终于读到第26章(全书共30章)，盟军已经突破德国在诺曼底半岛的防线，下一步将是消灭残部，向巴黎进...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2281555/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2281555_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2281555_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2861516">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2861516/" class="title-link">Beevor的八成功力</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2861516"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3334245/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3334245-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3334245/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">雪地野狗</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-15"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-15 09:00:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2861516_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我猜测这书是有许多助手参与的，因为好几处描述重复，比如英军用倒插步枪挂钢盔来标识伤员。仍然保持Beevor强项，在大量资料中刨出有趣的细节和小故事堆在一起。但是不如斯大林格勒和柏林那两本读来顺畅。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2861516_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2861516_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










